      "created_at": "2016-05-14 11:15:39 UTC",
      "updated_at": "2016-05-14 11:15:39 UTC",
      "body": "For the sake of completeness, this is how `unmanagedSourceDirectories` is [defined by sbt by default](https://github.com/sbt/sbt/blob/bcd36599357eac5163be9c9d836fd4fdf068624b/main/src/main/scala/sbt/Defaults.scala#L209):\r\n```scala\r\nunmanagedSourceDirectories := makeCrossSources(\r\n  scalaSource.value, javaSource.value, scalaBinaryVersion.value, crossPaths.value)\r\n```"
    }
